{
  "stem": "935.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I was behind John, and to stop and wait.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And John was going in first, and he talked to the soldier.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And he put a handful of bills-- not a handful-- it was a whole package, into this guy's hand.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And the thing-- the rail-- opened, and we just walked through.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And it seemed so ridiculous for us to go through all this baloney to just walk through the gate like nothing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And then we were on Belgian soil.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "However, Belgium was occupied too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It was also occupied country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Even so, the rumor had it it was much easier there because King Leopold II, who then reigned, had, just before the Nazis-- the Germans-- marched in, burned all the papers.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "In Europe, you need to register with the police.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Not only a foreigner, everybody needs to.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In other words, they know always where you are, what you do, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There is a national registry where you can find out exactly if you're looking for someone, for $0.50, who, where, what?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "King Leopold had it all destroyed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were no papers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In other words, it was much easier for a Belgian Jew to slip through the fingers, at least for a long, long time, than for a Dutch Jew.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know why the Dutch didn't do it, because they were so wonderful in many other ways.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was all there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's how they found everybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had it right here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On a little index card.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They could find out everybody's name, where they lived, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were in Belgium, and we could, they said, go on to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the train ride was absolutely ridiculous.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like a-- like an adventure film.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
